data.description: Charming & surprisingly spacious 3 bed/2 full bath ranch home featuring a partially finished basement, 2-car attached garage, & a massive 27x16 family room - all located on a large corner lot near the city park! The front room has a giant picture window that fills the space with light & a cozy knotty pine fireplace. Plentiful counter space in the kitchen with/an opening to the formal dining room. Great view to the backyard through the patio doors that lead to the private back patio area. Previously a 1-car garage, the huge family room is the PERFECT gathering space for entertaining! The sizeable master bedroom is located at the back of the home w/ double closets & en suite bath. But wait, there is even MORE space in the partially finished basement! Two concrete driveways allow for extra parking space, a utility shed for additional storage, mature trees/landscaping surround the home, & a charming stone exterior provides some timeless curb appeal! Don't miss your chance, call today and make this your next home!
